  <section class="docs-block">
    <h3 class="docs-heading">// MEET SOPHIE</h3>
    <p>Sophie is the AI voice receptionist behind this project -- the voice you'll hear on the call.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="docs-block">
    <h3 class="docs-heading">// WHAT IT DOES</h3>
    <p>Sophie answers inbound calls and handles them in natural conversation: she identifies the caller, answers questions about services, pricing, and hours from a fixed knowledge base, and books, reschedules, or cancels appointments against a real calendar -- reading the details back to confirm. Every call is saved automatically (transcript, outcome, recording).</p>
  </section>

  <section class="docs-block">
    <h3 class="docs-heading">// HEAR IT</h3>
    <p>Play a recorded demo call on this page and follow a full booking from greeting to confirmation.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="docs-block">
    <h3 class="docs-heading">// GOOD TO KNOW</h3>
    <p>Demo on a fictional business (GreenScape Landscaping). The agent isn't on a public line -- what you hear is a recorded real call.</p>
  </section>

</div>
